videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield drives to the rim and is swatted away by Reed Nikko to protect Missouri's first-half lead.
videos.headline: Missouri's Nikko meets Schofield at rim for big block

videos.description: Tennessee's Kyle Alexander throws an Xavier Pinson layup away, as Jordan Bowden collects the miss and throws down the breakaway dunk with authority.
videos.headline: Alexander's savage block leads to Bowden's punch dunk for Vols

videos.description: John Fulkerson drives to the cup and drops the hammer on the left-handed dunk for Tennessee.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Fulkerson flushes the lefty jam

videos.description: Grant Williams is quickly double teamed on the block and zips a pass to Kyle Alexander inside for the stuff to extend the Vols' lead.
videos.headline: Williams carves up double team with dime inside for Tennessee
